<div class="jumbotron">
  <h2><b>Level 2 - Four Tutorials</b></h2>
  <h3><b><%= @user.first_name.capitalize %></b>, you have passed the first level of acceptance
to become an official Rails Girl :)</h3>

<h2>The Second Level, if you choose to accept</h2>
<p>is to complete the 4 tutorials below that will help you
get the most out of the Rails Girls workshop and determine your acceptance.
</p>

<p style= "font-size:15px">Contact railsgirlsla@gmail.com with any further questions.</b></p>
